This is the definition of the fields for the customer screen:
-- First Name - char limit 50 char
-- Last Name - char limit 70 char
-- address - char limit 50
-- state - char limit 2 (set as a selection field with state abreviations)
-- zip - number limit 5 
-- email - char limit 255 w/validation of the @ symbol
-- phone - number limit 10 w/format (xxx-xxx-xxxx)
